14.1.3 igraph_layout_graphopt -- Optimizes vertex layout via the graphopt algorithm.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


     int igraph_layout_graphopt(const igraph_t *graph, igraph_matrix_t *res,
     			   igraph_integer_t niter,
